<episodedetails><title>La casa Milà</title><plot>The Casa Milà by Antoni Gaudi
A block of flats in Barcelona, the Casa Milà is an extraordinarily sculpted work created by the great Spanish architect Antoni Gaudi. The Art Nouveau apartments are Expressionistic, fantastic, organic forms with undulating facades and roof lines.</plot></episodedetails>